com.percussion.services.workflow.data
Class PSTransitionRole

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.services.workflow.data.PSTransitionRole
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSCatalogIdentifier, IPSCatalogItem, Serializable
public class PSTransitionRole
extends Object
implements Serializable, IPSCatalogItem

Represents associations between transitions and workflow roles. Required because using an @JoinTable annotation doesn't work with PSWORKFLOWAPPID on both sides of the join table due to Hiberate bug HHH-1338 (see http://opensource2.atlassian.com/projects/hibernate/browse/HHH-1338).
